window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After a thousand dates and hookups, I'd given up....</b></p> <p>....then the doorbell rang.</p> <p>Michael was a newborn gay not too many years ago. His first date was accidental. The ones that followed were adventures.</p> <p>Now, in his 30s, he wonders if finding a lasting relationship is even possible. Frustrated by the internet's failure to help him find true love, Michael swears off dating and decides to focus on his career.</p> <p>Then Heath shows up and rolls on the floor with Michael's furry best friend. The normally wary pup instantly falls for the irresistible stranger, but will Michael's heart bloom with also passion?</p> <p><b>You'll love this book because everyone dreams of a happy ending.</b></p> <p>Join Michael's journey today!</p> <p><i>My Last Date</i> is the final volume in the hilariously cheeky, best-selling <b>Raised by Wolves series</b>, a contemporary MM romance series about a newborn gay finding himself, told in the author's own voice. It explores the fullness of life, including hurt/comfort, found family, sexual awakening, love, loss and rebirth--and a guy who <i>finally</i> realizes who he is and what he wants.</p>"; 
